bcc-scene.title: BCC Scene
bcc-scene.description: Add custom text 'scenes' anywhere in the RedM game world. Whether you want to create immersive NPC dialogue, display important quest information, or simply add some flavor text to enhance the game world's atmosphere, bcc-scene is the perfect solution.

bcc-anticheat.title: BCC AntiCheat
bcc-anticheat.description: Our AntiCheat script provides comprehensive protection against a wide range of cheats and exploits With real-time monitoring, our AntiCheat script can quickly identify and flag suspicious behavior, ensuring a safe game experience for all players.

bcc-pets.title: BCC Pets
bcc-pets.description: Adopt your favorite pets and have them follow you around the game world. Whether you want a loyal dog by your side, a playful cat to keep you company, or a majestic toad to venture into battle, our Pet Adoption System has you covered.

bcc-pets.title: BCC Pets
bcc-pets.description: Adopt your favorite pets and have them follow you around the game world. Whether you want a loyal dog by your side, a playful cat to keep you company, or a majestic toad to venture into battle, our Pet Adoption System has you covered.

bcc-legendaries.title: BCC Legendaries
bcc-legendaries.description: A customizable hunting script that offers a quest-style format for players to hunt Legendary Animals. It includes a user-friendly menu, rewards for skinning the animal, a leveling system, and a built-in skinning system. The script is easily configurable and editable, and includes a version check system.

bcc-oil.title: BCC Oil
bcc-oil.description: Features a custom NUI menu, a level system, and the ability to own and use an oil and supply wagon. The script also allows you to undertake oil delivery, supply delivery, and oil wagon stealing missions, as well as rob the oil company. This script is highly customizable through the config.lua file.

bcc-nazar.title: BCC Nazar
bcc-nazar.description: Add Madam Nazar to your RedM server with features like treasure hunts and a black market. You can buy, sell, and get hints for treasure chests from Madam Nazar. The treasure hunts are on a global cooldown and you can customize the currency used in her shop.

bcc-farming.title: BCC Farming
bcc-farming.description: Looking to add some farming fun to your RedM server? Check out bcc-farming! Our easy-to-use script allows you to create multiple crops, lock them by job, and even save progress after server restarts. Plus, with features like watering prompts and blips on plants, you'll have a blast tending to your virtual garden.

bcc-acidtrip.title: BCC Acid Trip
bcc-acidtrip.description: Ready for a wild adventure? Introducing bcc-acidtrip, a trippy script for RedM that will take you on a journey you won't forget! With a 1 in 4 chance of a wacky hallucination-filled bad trip or a 3 in 4 chance of a euphoric high, you never know what you're going to get. Configurable and easy to set up, this script will bring some unexpected fun to your server. Come and experience the ride with bcc-acidtrip!

rdr3-nativedb-data.title: RDR3 Native Data
rdr3-nativedb-data.description: Scommunity maintained database of RDR3 information, specifically to power the redlookup.com

bcc-serverpassword.title: BCC Server Password
bcc-serverpassword.description: A handy tool that lets you secure your server with a password on join. You can set a case-sensitive password that kicks players out after a set time limit, limits password retries, and even bans players after multiple retries. It's easy to install and works seamlessly with your existing resources.

bcc-loadscreen.title: BCC Loadscreen
bcc-loadscreen.description: Upgrade your RedM server's loading screen with customized videos, images, and audio using our script! It's easy to install and supports local and web content. Plus, with 12 preset CSS loading icons and a time elapsed display, your players will always know when they're ready to jump in and start playing.

bcc-job-alerts.title: BCC Job Alerts
bcc-job-alerts.description: A job-based alert/ping system designed for RedM/Vorp servers. It comes with customizable commands that allow players to alert specific job roles such as Doctor or Police.

bcc-blindfold.title: BCC Blindfold
bcc-blindfold.description: Add a new level of excitement to your RedM and VorpCore Framework games with the blindfold script! Blindfold the nearest player or even yourself with easy commands and customizable features.

bcc-deferralcards.title: BCC Deferral Cards
bcc-deferralcards.description: A RedM library to make the use of Microsoft Adaptive Cards with deferrals easy for any developer.

bcc-crypt.title: BCC Crypt
bcc-crypt.description: A library for RedM developers that offers various encryption, decryption, hashing, and compression functionalities. By utilizing these features, RedM developers can enhance the security, performance, and functionality of their scripts.

bcc-vehiclefixes.title: BCC Vehicle Fixes
bcc-vehiclefixes.description: Say goodbye to stuck wagons and unwanted NPC boats with BCC Vehicle Fixes! This RedM script provides bug fixes for vehicles, making the game more enjoyable for players.

bcc-versioner.title: BCC Versioner
bcc-versioner.description: An API that allows developers to check the latest version of their custom scripts on GitHub. With Release(Tag) and Version File based checks, you can easily ensure your players are running the most up-to-date version of your script.

bcc-discord.title: BCC Discord
bcc-discord.description: Seamlessly send important server updates and messages straight to your Discord server using the magic of webhooks.

redowl.title: RedOwl
redowl.description: A Status Alert bot for your discord server! Keep your discord community up-to-date with any cfx outage live and with ease.

redlookup.title: RedLookup
redlookup.description: our NEW go to place for easy, up-to-date, Red Dead asset and native searching. RedLookup provides a completely searchable database of assets and natives for Red Dead 2 modding.
